<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header id="header">
        <div id="logo">
            <h1>LOGO</h1>
            <div id="search-bar">
                <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="Search...">
                <button type="submit" id="search-button">Search</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav id="nav-bar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" id="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" id="nav-link">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/cart" id="nav-link">Cart</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" id="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        
    </header>
    <main class="about-container">
            <section class="about-hero">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p>Welcome to our online store, where quality meets convenience.</p>
            </section>
    
            <section class="about-content">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2023, we've been committed to providing exceptional products and service to our customers. Our journey began with a simple idea: to make quality shopping accessible to everyone.</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>We strive to deliver the best shopping experience through carefully curated products, competitive prices, and outstanding customer service.</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h2>Our Values</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Customer Satisfaction</li>
                        <li>Quality Products</li>
                        <li>Integrity</li>
                        <li>Innovation</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
    
            <section class="team-section">
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <div class="team-grid">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="/images/team1.jpg" alt="Team Member">
                        <h3>John Doe</h3>
                        <p>CEO</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="/images/team2.jpg" alt="Team Member">
                        <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                        <p>Operations Manager</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="/images/team3.jpg" alt="Team Member">
                        <h3>Mike Johnson</h3>
                        <p>Customer Service Lead</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
    
            <style>
                .about-container {
                    max-width: 1200px;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                    padding: 20px;
                }
    
                .about-hero {
                    text-align: center;
                    padding: 60px 20px;
                    background-color: #f5f5f5;
                    margin-bottom: 40px;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                }
    
                .about-hero h1 {
                    font-size: 2.5em;
                    color: #333;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
    
                .about-content {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
                    gap: 30px;
                    margin-bottom: 40px;
                }
    
                .about-card {
                    background: white;
                    padding: 25px;
                    border-radius: 8px;
                    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
                }
    
                .about-card:hover {
                    transform: translateY(-5px);
                }
    
                .about-card h2 {
                    color: #333;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                }
    
                .about-card ul {
                    list-style-type: none;
                    padding-left: 0;
                }
    
                .about-card ul li {
                    margin: 10px 0;
                    padding-left: 20px;
                    position: relative;
                }
    
                .about-card ul li:before {
                    content: "â€¢";
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 0;
                    color: #4CAF50;
                }
    
                .team-section {
                    text-align: center;
                    margin-top: 60px;
                }
    
                .team-section h2 {
                    margin-bottom: 40px;
                }
    
                .team-grid {
                    display: grid;
                    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
                    gap: 30px;
                    margin-top: 30px;
                }
    
                .team-member {
                    background: white;
                    padding: 20px;
                    border-radius: 8px;
                    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                }
    
                .team-member img {
                    width: 150px;
                    height: 150px;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    object-fit: cover;
                    margin-bottom: 15px;
                }
    
                .team-member h3 {
                    color: #333;
                    margin: 10px 0 5px;
                }
    
                .team-member p {
                    color: #666;
                    margin: 0;
                }
    
                @media (max-width: 768px) {
                    .about-hero {
                        padding: 40px 20px;
                    }
    
                    .about-hero h1 {
                        font-size: 2em;
                    }
    
                    .about-content {
                        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                    }
    
                    .team-grid {
                        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                    }
                }
            </style>
        </main>
    
</body>
</html>